tion-attachment-24781\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24781\" src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/vi-tri-du-an-can-ho-west-gate.jpg\" alt=\"V tr vng West Gate ngay ti trung tm hnh chnh tnh Bnh Chnh\" width=\"1300\" height=\"981\" /></noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-24781\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V tr vng West Gate ngay ti trung tm hnh chnh tnh Bnh Chnh</p></div><div id=\"attachment_22339\" style=\"width: 1310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22339\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22339\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%20viewBox=\'0%200%201300%20562\'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" alt=\"V tr d n West Gate ngay ti khu Trung Tm Bnh Chnh \" width=\"1300\" height=\"562\" data-lazy-src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/vi-tri-du-an-west-gate-binh-chanh-chu-dau-tu-an-gia.jpg\"><noscript><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22339\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22339\" src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/vi-tri-du-an-west-gate-binh-chanh-chu-dau-tu-an-gia.jpg\" alt=\"V tr d n West Gate ngay ti khu Trung Tm Bnh Chnh \" width=\"1300\" height=\"562\" /></noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-22339\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kt ni khu vc West Gate Bnh Chnh v cng tin li</p></div><p></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bnh Chnh nm  ca ng pha Ty v pha Nam kt ni TP. H Ch Minh vi cc tnh ng bng sng Cu Long. Khu vc ny c hng li nh quy hoch bi bn, ng b vi khu hnh chnh trung tm, nhiu cng trnh h tng k thut, h tng x hi. Bnh Chnh tp trung dn c ln, tc   th ha nhanh, nhiu khu cng nghip nh Tn To, Phong Ph, L Minh Xun v nhiu ng giao thng huyt mch.</p><div id=\"attachment_22338\" style=\"width: 1310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22338\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22338\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%20viewBox=\'0%200%201300%20658\'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" alt=\"Tin ch ngoi khu ca d n West Gate B