(182, 1, '2020-03-05 10:03:21', '2020-03-05 10:03:21', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cng thuc khun kh bi quan trng nn mnh cng xin vit li v vn  ny do hai bi c kia hin nay hi li thi v mt s cp nht trong WordPress 3.8.1.  bi ny, mnh s hng dn chi tit nhng ngn gn v khi nim&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/tag/custom-post-type\">Custom Post Type</a>&nbsp;v cch lm vic vi Custom Post Type thng qua code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\">Custom Post Type l g?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":13652,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/custom_post_types.gif\"><img src=\"https://thachpham.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/custom_post_types.gif\" alt=\"Hng dn Custom Post Type\" class=\"wp-image-13652\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc nh trong WordPress s cho bn&nbsp;<strong>Page</strong>&nbsp;v&nbsp;<strong>Post</strong>&nbsp; xut bn ni dung v hai ci ny c gi l&nbsp;<strong>post type</strong>. Nu bn c nhu cu s dng nhiu hn 2 post type, v d lm thm mt post type khc vi mc ch ng sn phm th bt buc chng ta phi t to mt post type tng ng, v ci post type m do chng ta t to ra th c gi l&nbsp;<strong>Custom Post Type</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt Custom Post Type s hon ton c  nhng t cht ging ht nh hai post type mc nh, ngha l bn c th s dng&nbsp;<em>category</em>,&nbsp;<em>tag</em>,&nbsp;<em>custom field</em>,&nbsp;<em>featured image</em>,.v c th gi hin th ra ngoi trang ch cng lc vi Post.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-2\">Cch to Custom Post Type</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hy nn nh rng, hin nay t ai to custom post type bng cch g tng dng code nh trong bi ny m s s dng cc cng c m mnh s  cp  cui bi, do  c th bn khng cn nh ht cc tham s khi to. Nhng cc bn lu  dm mnh l hy c k bi  hiu quy trnh to mt custom post type nh th no  d dng khi lm vic v sau.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ging nh lm vic vi cc code&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wordpress/wordpress-development/huong-dan-tao-widget.html\">to widget&nbsp;</a>hay&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wordpress/wordpress-development/cach-tao-shortcode-tu-a-toi-z.html\">to shortcode</a>,  to mt custom post type bn c th vit vo file functions.php ca theme hoc to plugin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> to custom post type ta c cu trc code nh sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>0102030405060708091011121314</td><td><code>function</code> <code>tao_custom_post_type() {</code>&nbsp;<code>/*</code><code>* Bin $args l nhng tham s quan trng trong Post Type</code><code>*/</code><code>$args</code> <code>= </code><code>array</code><code>(</code><code>//Tham s cu hnh cho custom post type</code><code>);</code>&nbsp;<code>register_post_type( </code><code>\'slug-post-type\'</code> <code>, </code><code>$args</code> <code>); </code><code>//Ci slug-post-type rt quan trng, bn c th t ty  nhng khng c du cch, k t,...</code>&nbsp;<code>}</code>&nbsp;<code>add_action( </code><code>\'init\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'tao_custom_post_type\'</code> <code>);</code></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng c g l kh hiu, u tin l ta s to mt hm ring  to custom post type v cui cng ny l kch hot ci hm ny vo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wordpress/wordpress-development/cach-su-dung-action-hook-trong-wordpress.html\">action hook</a>&nbsp;<code>init</code>&nbsp;l xong.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong hm tao_custom_post_type() l mt hm&nbsp;<code>register_post_type()</code>&nbsp; khi to custom post type vi cc tham s m ta s khai bo trong bin&nbsp;<code>$args</code>. Th l ht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> l cu trc, quan trng l ta s khai bo nhng g trong . Bn c th xem qua cc tham s ti&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Function_Reference/register_post_type\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">register_post_type  WordPress Codex</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-3\">Cc tham s trong code to Custom Post Type</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Di y l cch khai bo tham s quan trng nht, nhng tham s dng optional mnh s b qua.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gi s mnh cn to mt custom post type  ng sn phm th s c code nh sau.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>01020304050607080910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031323334353637383940414243444546474849</td><td><code>function</code> <code>tao_custom_post_type()</code><code>{</code>&nbsp;<code>/*</code><code>* Bin $label  cha cc text lin quan n tn hin th ca Post Type trong Admin</code><code>*/</code><code>$label</code> <code>= </code><code>array</code><code>(</code><code>\'name\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>\'Cc sn phm\'</code><code>, </code><code>//Tn post type dng s nhiu</code><code>\'singular_name\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>\'Sn phm\'</code> <code>//Tn post type dng s t</code><code>);</code>&nbsp;<code>/*</code><code>* Bin $args l nhng tham s quan trng trong Post Type</code><code>*/</code><code>$args</code> <code>= </code><code>array</code><code>(</code><code>\'labels\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>$label</code><code>, </code><code>//Gi cc label trong bin $label  trn</code><code>\'description\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>\'Post type ng sn phm\'</code><code>, </code><code>//M t ca post type</code><code>\'supports\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>array</code><code>(</code><code>\'title\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'editor\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'excerpt\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'author\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'thumbnail\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'comments\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'trackbacks\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'revisions\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'custom-fields\'</code><code>), </code><code>//Cc tnh nng c h tr trong post type</code><code>\'taxonomies\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>array</code><code>( </code><code>\'category\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'post_tag\'</code> <code>), </code><code>//Cc taxonomy c php s dng  phn loi ni dung</code><code>\'hierarchical\'</code> <code>=&gt; false, </code><code>//Cho php phn cp, nu l false th post type ny ging nh Post, true th ging nh Page</code><code>\'public\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Kch hot post type</code><code>\'show_ui\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Hin th khung qun tr nh Post/Page</code><code>\'show_in_menu\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Hin th trn Admin Menu (tay tri)</code><code>\'show_in_nav_menus\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Hin th trong Appearance -&gt; Menus</code><code>\'show_in_admin_bar\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Hin th trn thanh Admin bar mu en.</code><code>\'menu_position\'</code> <code>=&gt; 5, </code><code>//Th t v tr hin th trong menu (tay tri)</code><code>\'menu_icon\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>\'\'</code><code>, </code><code>//ng dn ti icon s hin th</code><code>\'can_export\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//C th export ni dung bng Tools -&gt; Export</code><code>\'has_archive\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Cho php lu tr (month, date, year)</code><code>\'exclude_from_search\'</code> <code>=&gt; false, </code><code>//Loi b khi kt qu tm kim</code><code>\'publicly_queryable\'</code> <code>=&gt; true, </code><code>//Hin th cc tham s trong query, phi t true</code><code>\'capability_type\'</code> <code>=&gt; </code><code>\'post\'</code> <code>//</code><code>);</code>&nbsp;<code>register_post_type(</code><code>\'sanpham\'</code><code>, </code><code>$args</code><code>); </code><code>//To post type vi slug tn l sanpham v cc tham s trong bin $args  trn</code>&nbsp;<code>}</code><code>/* Kch hot hm to custom post type */</code><code>add_action(</code><code>\'init\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'tao_custom_post_type\'</code><code>);</code></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gii thch th trong code mnh  gii thch kh chi tit ri nn  y mnh khng ni li, mnh ch cn bn   gip&nbsp;<code>register_post_type( \'sanpham\', $args )</code>&nbsp;v  l on khi to Custom Post Type vi tn l&nbsp;<code>sanpham</code>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kt qu ta c</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":13651,\"linkDestination\":\"custom\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/demo-custom-post-type-2014.jpg\"><img src=\"https://thachpham.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/demo-custom-post-type-2014.jpg\" alt=\"demo-custom-post-type-2014\" class=\"wp-image-13651\"/></a></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Woooot!!! Thnh cng ri ha, r chut vo bn cng thy phn xem tt c cc post bn trong post type  v nt Add new  thm post mi ging nh Page/Post. Vy l coi nh bn  to xong mt Custom Post Type ri .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-4\">Hin th custom post type ra trang ch</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc nh nu ngoi trang ch bn ang hin th danh sch cc post mi nht th n ch ly bi trong Post hin th ch khng ly post ca mt custom post type ra,  cho n hin th bn ch cn chn thm dng ny vo functions.php</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>010203040506</td><td><code>add_filter(</code><code>\'pre_get_posts\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'lay_custom_post_type\'</code><code>);</code><code>function</code> <code>lay_custom_post_type(</code><code>$query</code><code>) {</code><code>if</code> <code>(is_home() &amp;&amp; </code><code>$query</code><code>-&gt;is_main_query ())</code><code>$query</code><code>-&gt;set (</code><code>\'post_type\'</code><code>, </code><code>array</code> <code>(</code><code>\'post\'</code><code>,</code><code>\'sanpham\'</code><code>));</code><code>return</code> <code>$query</code><code>;</code><code>}</code></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn nh thay&nbsp;<code>sanpham</code>&nbsp;thnh tn slug ca custom post type bn va to nh.  l l do v sao mnh ku bn nh ci slug ny, cn nhiu vic  dng na.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-5\">To file hin th ni dung custom post type</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Da vo cu trc ca theme, th mc nh custom post type s hin th da theo code ca file single.php trong theme. Nu bn mun n hin th khc, th c to mt file tn l&nbsp;<strong>single-{slug-post-type}.php</strong>. Nh v d ny th mnh s to file tn l&nbsp;<em>single-sanpham.php</em>&nbsp; hin th ni dung trong post type ring ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn c th copy ton b code bn file single.php qua file mi to ny v sa li cho nhanh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-6\">S dng trong Loop</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> hin th danh sch cc bi trong mt custom post type ra ngoi bng&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wordpress/wordpress-development/tim-hieu-wordpress-query-va-loop.html\">Loop &amp; Query</a>&nbsp;th ch cn khai bo thm mt tham s post_type vo l c. V d:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>01</td><td><code>$new_query</code> <code>= </code><code>new</code> <code>WP_Query( </code><code>\'post_type=sanpham\'</code> <code>);</code></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu d dng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-7\">Cng c to Custom Post Type nhanh</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nh mnh  ni  u bi, by gi t ai to Custom Post Type m vit tng dng code m thay vo  l s dng cc cng c to cho nhanh bi v thc t bc to n cng ch c nhiu  ch khng khc hn. Di y l cc cng c m bn nn xem qua:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong><a href=\"http://generatewp.com/post-type/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Custom Post Type Generator</a></strong>&nbsp; Cho php bn to custom post type nhanh chng bng vic chn mt s ty chn c sn v ly ton b code v. Bn ch cn copy on code ny vo file functions.php hoc lm plugin ring l xong.</li><li><strong><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/custom-post-type-ui/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Custom Post Type UI&nbsp;</a></strong> Plugin min ph cho php to custom post type nhanh chng trc tip trong WP-Admin.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vy thi, cn cc cng c khc n nhiu tnh nng qu nn mnh khng  cp ti v rt hi no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"ftoc-heading-8\">Kt bi</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong bi ny mnh ch  cp n y thi v mnh ngh nhiu   qu   cho bn hiu Custom Post Type l g v cch to n. D nhin cn rt l nhiu tips/tricks  chng ta s dng vi chc nng ny nhng nu c mnh s vit bi ring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hn na, khi lm vic vi Custom Post Type c th bn s phi tm hiu thm mt khi nim khc na,  l&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wordpress/wordpress-development/wordpress-custom-taxonomy-toan-tap.html\">Custom Taxonomies</a>&nbsp;m mnh s  cp  bi tip theo v sau khi c bi  ri mnh s  cp ti mt s th thut lin quan n Custom Post Type, t  bn s d dng hiu m khng phi qu nng u c.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Movie test', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'movie-test', '', '', '2020-03-05 10:03:21', '2020-03-05 10:03:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jnews/?post_type=movie&#038;p=182', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
