(183, 1, '2020-03-05 10:11:44', '2020-03-05 10:11:44', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>LM TRANG SHOP N GIN VI WORDPRESS  07</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>bi&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/author/phamngocthach\">Thch Phm</a><a href=\"https://thachpham.com/giveaway/uu-dai-tu-azdigi-danh-rieng-cho-doc-gia-tai-thachpham-com.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cho mng bn n vi phn cui trong serie to shop n gin trn m ngun WordPress bng vic p dng kin thc&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/tag/custom-post-type\">custom post type</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://thachpham.com/wordpress/wordpress-development/wordpress-custom-taxonomy-toan-tap.html\">custom taxonomy</a>&nbsp;v meta box. Trong phn ny, chng ta s lm mt vic cui cng  l to template hin th trang danh sch cc sn phm (hay cn gi l trang lu tr ca custom post type) v template hin th trang ni dung ca danh mc sn phm (cn gi l trang lu tr cho taxonomy).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\">TRANG LU TR SN PHM</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti trang ny, chng ta s cho hin th ton b cc d liu trong custom post type&nbsp;<code>sanpham</code>&nbsp;m chng ta  to ra. Theo cu trc template ca WordPress, chng ta s s dng tp tin&nbsp;<strong>archive-sanpham.php</strong>&nbsp; hin th. Nhng hin ti tp tin ny cha c nn ta s copy t tp tin archive.php trong theme  m bo tun th theo cu trc ca theme.<strong>Lu </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> trang lu tr sn phm hot ng, trong code to custom post type phi c tham s has_archive vi gi tr l true.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By gi hy copy tp tin&nbsp;<em>/sparkling/archive.php</em>&nbsp;sang&nbsp;<em>/sparkling-child/archive-sanpham.php</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau  tm on ny v xa i v khng cn thit  hin th:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>0102030405060708091011121314151617181920212223242526272829303132333435363738394041424344454647484950515253545556575859606162</td><td><code>&lt;header </code><code>class</code><code>=</code><code>\"page-header\"</code><code>&gt;</code><code>&lt;h1 </code><code>class</code><code>=</code><code>\"page-title\"</code><code>&gt;</code><code>&lt;?php</code><code>if</code> <code>( is_category() ) :</code><code>single_cat_title();</code>&nbsp;<code>elseif</code> <code>( is_tag() ) :</code><code>single_tag_title();</code>&nbsp;<code>elseif</code> <code>( is_author() ) :</code><code>printf( esc_html__( </code><code>\'Author: %s\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'sparkling\'</code> <code>), </code><code>\'&lt;span class=\"vcard\"&gt;\'</code> <code>. get_the_author() . </code><code>\'&lt;/span&gt;\'</code> <code>);</code>&nbsp;<code>elseif</code> <code>( is_day() ) :</code><code>printf( esc_html__( </code><code>\'Day: %s\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'sparkling\'</code> <code>), </code><code>\'&lt;span&gt;\'</code> <code>. get_the_date() . </code><code>\'&lt;/span&gt;\'</code> <code>);</code>&nbsp;<code>elseif</code> <code>( is_month() ) :</code><code>printf( esc_html__( </code><code>\'Month: %s\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'sparkling\'</code> <code>), </code><code>\'&lt;span&gt;\'</code> <code>. get_the_date( _x( </code><code>\'F Y\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'monthly archives date format\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'sparkling\'</code> <code>) ) . </code><code>\'&lt;/span&gt;\'</code> <code>);</code>&nbsp;<code>elseif</code> <code>( is_year() ) :</code><code>printf( esc_html__( </code><code>\'Year: %s\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'sparkling\'</code> <code>), </code><code>\'&lt;span&gt;\'</code> <code>. get_the_date( _x( </code><code>\'Y\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'yearly archives date format\'</code><code>, </code><code>\'sparkling\'</code> <code>) ) . </code><code>\'&lt;/span&gt;\'<