caption-attachment-24781\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24781\" src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/vi-tri-du-an-can-ho-west-gate.jpg\" alt=\"V tr vng West Gate ngay ti trung tm hnh chnh tnh Bnh Chnh\" width=\"1300\" height=\"981\" /></noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-24781\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V tr vng West Gate ngay ti trung tm hnh chnh tnh Bnh Chnh</p></div><div id=\"attachment_22339\" style=\"width: 1310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22339\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22339\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%20viewBox=\'0%200%201300%20562\'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" alt=\"V tr d n West Gate ngay ti khu Trung Tm Bnh Chnh \" width=\"1300\" height=\"562\" data-lazy-src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/vi-tri-du-an-west-gate-binh-chanh-chu-dau-tu-an-gia.jpg\"><noscript><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22339\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22339\" src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/vi-tri-du-an-west-gate-binh-chanh-chu-dau-tu-an-gia.jpg\" alt=\"V tr d n West Gate ngay ti khu Trung Tm Bnh Chnh \" width=\"1300\" height=\"562\" /></noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-22339\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kt ni khu vc West Gate Bnh Chnh v cng tin li</p></div><p></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bnh Chnh nm  ca ng pha Ty v pha Nam kt ni TP. H Ch Minh vi cc tnh ng bng sng Cu Long. Khu vc ny c hng li nh quy hoch bi bn, ng b vi khu hnh chnh trung tm, nhiu cng trnh h tng k thut, h tng x hi. Bnh Chnh tp trung dn c ln, tc   th ha nhanh, nhiu khu cng nghip nh Tn To, Phong Ph, L Minh Xun v nhiu ng giao thng huyt mch.</p><div id=\"attachment_22338\" style=\"width: 1310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22338\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22338\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%20viewBox=\'0%200%201300%20658\'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" alt=\"Tin ch ngoi khu ca d n West Gate Bnh Chnh\" width=\"1300\" height=\"658\" data-lazy-src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tien-ich-ngoai-khu-du-an-west-gate-binh-chanh.jpg\"><noscript><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22338\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22338\" src=\"//angialand.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/tien-ich-ngoai-khu-du-an-west-gate-binh-chanh.jpg\" alt=\"Tin ch ngoi khu ca d n West Gate Bnh Chnh\" width=\"1300\" height=\"658\" /></noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-22338\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tin ch ngoi khu ca d n West Gate Bnh Chnh</p></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo lnh o Thnh ph H Ch Minh, Bnh Chnh  t a s cc tiu ch  ln qun t nm 2012. Bnh Chnh hin ang u t vo d n c quy m, nhiu tin ch ni khu nh b bi, khu th thao,  p ng nhu cu sng theo phong cch hin i ca c dn khu vc.&nbsp;Trong thi gian ti d kin trc nm 2020, Quc l 50 s c m rng v xy dng ng song hnh QL50 di 8,6km ( c thnh ph ph duyt)  thng thong giao thng.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><div role=\"form\" class=\"wpcf7\" id=\"wpcf7-f10069-o15\" lang=\"en-US\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"screen-reader-response\"></div><form action=\"/can-ho/can-ho-binh-chanh/west-gate-park#wpcf7-f10069-o15\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form\" novalidate=\"novalidate\"><div style=\"display: none;\"> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"10069\"> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"5.1.6\"> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"en_US\"> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f10069-o15\"> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_container_post\" value=\"0\"></div><div class=\"formbv\"><p>Nhn Bo Gi v Khuyn Mi chi tit t ch u t</p><div class=\"col-md-2\"><span class=\"wpcf7-form-control-wrap your-name\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"your-name\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"wpcf7-form-control wpcf7-text wpcf7-validates-as-required\" aria-required=\"true\" aria-invalid=\"false\" placeholder=\"Tn (*)\"></span></div><div class=\"col-md-2\"><span clas