(1142, 1, '2020-03-20 04:08:55', '2020-03-20 04:08:55', '<em><strong>Hin nay, th trng Bt ng Sn Khu Nam n nhn mn trnh lng y n tng ca d n cn h West Gate Bnh Chnh. Cn h l ni tinh hoa t tri hi t, ni con ngi khng ch n thun l sng. West Gate Park Bnh Chnh mang n nhng tin ch ng cp hng u vi phong cch kin trc nh cao.</strong></em>\n<em><strong>Vi li th ln khi nm ti v tr vng mt tin Nguyn Vn Linh, l cu ni ti cc trung tm hnh chnh, thng mi v gii tr ca TPHCM . y l v tr thun li cho c giao thng ng b v ng thy i vo trung tm thnh ph. Trong khu vc xy dng d n c mt bn cng hin do Cng Ty C Phn u T Tn Hng qun l v khai thc, l a im thun li  pht trin cc dch v vui chi gii tr di nc.</strong></em>\n\n<em><strong>Thay mt ch u t - phng kinh doanh xin gii thiu qu khch hng d n cn h west gate bnh chnh qua cc thng tin chi tit sau:</strong></em>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"tong-quan-west-gate-binh-chanh\"><strong>TNG QUAN WEST GATE BNH CHNH</strong></span></h2>\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-5dfbc5d2121ab fl-col-group-equal-height fl-col-group-align-center\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d2121ab\">\n<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-5dfbc5d2121e5 fl-col-has-cols\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d2121e5\">\n<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-5dfbc5d212708 fl-col-group-nested fl-col-group-equal-height fl-col-group-align-center\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d212708\">\n<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-5dfbc5d212742\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d212742\">\n<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-5dfbc5d21223d fl-animation fl-fade-left fl-animated\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d21223d\" data-animation-delay=\"0.0\" data-animation-duration=\"2\">\n<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n\n<strong> Tn d n</strong>: WEST GATE PARK\n\n<strong> Ch u t</strong>: Tp on Bt ng Sn An Gia (An Gia Investment)\n\n<strong> V tr:</strong>: Mt tin ng Nguyn Vn Linh,<a href=\"https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%ACnh_Ch%C3%A1nh\">Bnh Chnh</a>, TP H Ch Minh.\n\n<strong> Xy dng</strong>:\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Thit k</strong>: Architecture &amp; Design</li>\n 	<li><strong>Tng thu xy dng</strong>: Coteccons</li>\n 	<li><strong>Thi cng mng cc</strong>: Coteccons</li>\n 	<li><strong>Qun l v vn hnh</strong>: CBRE</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Quy m d n</strong>: 3,1 ha - cao 20 tng\n\n<strong>Loi hnh sn phm</strong>: Cn h, shophouse\n\n<strong>S lng</strong>: 1900 cn h\n\n<strong>Din tch</strong>: 50 - 74 m2 ( 2 phng ng) , 85 - 113 m2 ( 3 phng ng)\n\n<strong>Hnh thc s hu</strong>: S hu vnh vin ( i vi ngi nc ngoi s hu 50 nm)\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"TNG QUAN D N NAM LONG TAT BNH DNG\" class=\"fl-module fl-module-photo fl-node-5dfbc5d212277 fl-animation fl-fade-right fl-animated\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d212277\" data-animation-delay=\"0.0\" data-animation-duration=\"2\">\n<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-photo fl-photo-align-center\">\n<div class=\"fl-photo-content fl-photo-img-jpg\"><img class=\"fl-photo-img wp-image-6245\" title=\"TNG QUAN WEST GATE BNH CHNH\" src=\"https://namtrungland.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/97d126abbd4b44151d5a.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://namtrungland.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/97d126abbd4b44151d5a.jpg 1024w, https://namtrungland.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/97d126abbd4b44151d5a-300x205.jpg 300w, https://namtrungland.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/97d126abbd4b44151d5a-768x525.jpg 768w\" alt=\"TNG QUAN WEST GATE BNH CHNH\" />\n<div class=\"fl-photo-caption fl-photo-caption-hover\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-5dfbc5d2122b0\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d2122b0\">\n<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-5dfbc5d2122ea fl-col-has-cols\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d2122ea\">\n<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-separator fl-node-5dfbc5d212323\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d212323\">\n<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-separator\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"color: #1d1f20; font-size: 1.953em;\">V TR D N WEST GATE BNH CHNH</strong></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-5dfbc5d21235c fl-col-group-nested\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d21235c\">\n<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-5dfbc5d212396\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d212396\">\n<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-5dfbc5d2123d0 fl-animation fl-fade-up fl-animated\" data-node=\"5dfbc5d2123d0\" data-animation-delay=\"0.0\" data-animation-duration=\"2\">\n<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n<div class=\"sevenPostDes\">\n\n<strong>D n westgate bnh chnh</strong>nm trn huyn Bnh Chnh. T v tr ny c dn West Gate Bnh Chnh thun li di chuyn v Qun 7, 8, cc tnh min Ty, cc qun trung tm Thnh Ph nh sau:\n\n-<strong>Trung tm Qun 1</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>D n cn h Westgatepark</strong>-&gt; Trnh Quang Ngh -&gt; Nguyn Vn Linh -&gt; QL50 -&gt; V Vn Kit: 14,9km v thi gian trung bnh t 35  40 pht.\nTuyn ng ny cng p dng  i vo Qun 8 (5 pht), Qun 5(25 pht) hoc Qun 6 (35 pht).</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>- i v Qun 7</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Cn h West Gate An Gia Bnh Chnh</strong>-&gt; Trnh Quang Ngh -&gt; Nguyn Vn Linh: 20 pht di chuyn vi on ng di khong 10km.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>- i v Long An v cc tnh min Ty</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Cn h West Gate Binh Chanh</strong>-&gt; Trnh Quang Ngh -&gt; QL50: 15 pht di chuyn vi qung ng di 6.5km.Trn cc trc ng ny, cc tin ch phc v nhu cu sinh hot hng ngy nh bnh vin, trng hc, ch tp trung, trung tm thng mi, cc ca hng bn l rt d tip cn.</li>\n</ul>\nKhng ch c u th kt ni, v tr ca d n cn s hu nhiu tim nng tng gi bi y l khu vc sm ut, cng ng dn c vn minh, tr thc,, D n nm lin k cc khu dn c cao cp nn tha hng ton b h thng tin ch ngoi khu hon chnh, kin to cuc sng thnh vng.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"V TR D N NAM LONG TAT BNH DNG\" class=\